Available Tools: set_temperature | get_temperature | set_mode | get_schedule
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "device_id": "string", "temperature": "number|null", "mode": "string|null" }
Response Schema: { "device_id": "string", "current_temp": "number", "target_temp": "number", "mode": "string" }
---
Question: Adjust the kitchen thermostat to 23 degrees for cooking dinner.
Call: { "func_call": "set_temperature", "device_id": "therm_kit_09", "temperature": 23.0, "mode": null }
Response: { "device_id": "therm_kit_09", "current_temp": 21.5, "target_temp": 23.0, "mode": "heat" }

Question: Lower the sunroom temperature to 19 degrees before sunset.
Call: { "func_call": "set_temperature", "device_id": "therm_sun_10", "temperature": 19.0, "mode": null }
Response: { "device_id": "therm_sun_10", "current_temp": 24.3, "target_temp": 19.0, "mode": "cool" }

Question: Raise the attic unit to 25 degrees to prevent freezing pipes.
Call: { "func_call": "set_temperature", "device_id": "therm_att_11", "temperature": 25.0, "mode": null }
